Class
Description
Button
The `Button` class represents a concrete element in the composite structure.
CountElementsVisitor
The `CountElementsVisitor` class is a concrete visitor that implements the `Visitor` interface.
Element
The `Element` interface represents an element in the composite structure.
Main
The `Main` class serves as the entry point for the application, demonstrating the use of the Visitor pattern for counting the number of buttons within a composite structure of panels and buttons.
Panel
The `Panel` class represents a composite element in the composite structure.
Visitor
The `Visitor` interface declares methods for each concrete element type to be visited in the composite structure.
